  <div class="attributed-text-segment-list__container relative mt-1 mb-1.5 babybear:mt-0 babybear:mb-0.5">
    <p class="attributed-text-segment-list__content text-color-text !text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap break-words
        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">Hydrogen is no longer a future concept. It’s already here.  💧  

This week in Portugal 🇵🇹, at the international conference on hydrogen in vocational education, we worked with partners across Europe on a critical question:

Can our skills systems keep up with the speed of technological change?

At <a class="link" href="https://ee.linkedin.com/company/tartu-voco?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Tartu Rakenduslik Kolledž (Tartu Vocational College)</a>, this is exactly where we focus our work.
While hydrogen technologies are scaling rapidly - across production, storage, and mobility - the real bottleneck is no longer technology.
It’s people.
👉 Teachers not yet prepared to teach it
👉 Curricula still catching up
👉 Training systems moving slower than industry

That’s why our approach is simple:
We don’t just talk about hydrogen.
We translate it into teachable skills.

At the conference, I presented how we are doing this at <a class="link" href="https://ee.linkedin.com/company/tartu-voco?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Tartu Rakenduslik Kolledž (Tartu Vocational College)</a> - turning hydrogen and clean technologies into structured VET learning - through <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/h2cove?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>H2CoVE</a>, <a class="link" href="https://be.linkedin.com/in/green-skills-for-hydrogen-419555304?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Green Skills for Hydrogen</a>, and Auto-CoVE 2.0 initiatives.

Our focus is practical:
🔹 Training teachers through real, hands-on experience
🔹 Developing industry-relevant learning modules
🔹 Aligning education with actual workforce needs
🔹 Bringing new technologies into classrooms and workshops

Key takeaway:
Technology is ready. Skills are not.

And the reality is clear:
Vocational education is where this transition will either succeed  or fail.

🙏 Special thanks to <a class="link" href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/stefan-nowatschin-539558ba?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Stefan Nowatschin</a>, leader of the Network of Excellence in Vocational Education and Training for Sustainable Development, and to our host <a class="link" href="https://pt.linkedin.com/in/cristina-faria-dos-santos?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Cristina Faria dos Santos</a>, Director of CFAE Centro-Oeste, for the excellent organisation and strong collaboration.

Good to see real momentum across Europe 🇪🇺  and partners focused on making this transition work in practice.

Let’s build this together. 💪 

<a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fhydrogen&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Hydrogen</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fvet&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#VET</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fskills&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Skills</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fenergytransition&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#EnergyTransition</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fh2cove&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#H2CoVE</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fgreenskills&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#GreenSkills</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fautocove&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#AutoCoVE</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Ferasmusplus&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#ErasmusPlus</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fvocationaleducation&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#VocationalEducation</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/cop-coves?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>CoP CoVEs</a></p>
