The PUMP-UP project is hosting a series of FREE online seminars every Monday &amp; Wednesday (10:00–11:00 CEST) throughout May. Each session covers one module of the course, with a final session dedicated to teaching methods and didactics.

✅ Open to everyone
✅ Join as many sessions as you like
✅ Learn at your own pace

