    <p class="attributed-text-segment-list__content text-color-text !text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap break-words
        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">Have you registered yet?
Not yet…? Why wait! Secure your spot today and be part of something meaningful!

🗓️ Join us on Wed 20th of May | 13:00–14:00 (CET)
📍 Online event &amp; streamed live

Discover the final outcomes of the IMVET project and explore how we’re advancing inclusive international mobility.

What’s in it for you?
• Practical tools to support inclusive mobility programs
• A self-assessment resource for organizations
• Accessible materials for students with disabilities

