  <div class="attributed-text-segment-list__container relative mt-1 mb-1.5 babybear:mt-0 babybear:mb-0.5">
    <p class="attributed-text-segment-list__content text-color-text !text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap break-words
        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">🏆 VOCO Shines at International Skills Competition in Riga!
Big news from the international stage! From March 24–26, our talented students took part in the “Learn, Know, Do, Can, Show” skills competition in Riga, Latvia and the results were spectacular.
With 16 countries and 42 schools represented, VOCO stood among the best. 
🌟 Our Winners:
Salesmanship: Berit Viigipuu (Mentor: <a class="link" href="https://ee.linkedin.com/in/mariliismaremae?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Mariliis Maremäe</a>)
Classical Cooking: Eliis Sasmil (Mentors: Katrin Jurs, Kairi Timusk, Markus Pärn)
Vegan Culinary Art: Rannet Palmsaar (Mentors: Katrin Jurs, Kairi Timusk, Markus Pärn)
Confectionery: Alexandra Aljaste (Mentor: Lilija Suburg)
Meat Culinary: Tauri Koort (Mentor: <a class="link" href="https://ee.linkedin.com/in/kristi-luht-818b9337b?trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Kristi Luht</a>)
Meat Culinary: Artem Danko (Mentor: Kamilla Lüdikainen)
Tourism: Pärle Punger (Mentor: Ene Reedi)
A massive congratulations to all participants and a heartfelt thank you to the mentors who guided them to success. Your work truly matters! 

