  <div class="attributed-text-segment-list__container relative mt-1 mb-1.5 babybear:mt-0 babybear:mb-0.5">
    <p class="attributed-text-segment-list__content text-color-text !text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap break-words
        " dir="ltr" data-test-id="main-feed-activity-card__commentary">On 19 February, Tartu VOCO’s Engineering Academy hosted a professional training seminar titled “Teaching Hydrogen Technologies in Technical Vocational Education.” The event brought together vocational education and training (VET) teachers in technical fields from across Estonia.

The objective of the training was to strengthen teachers’ knowledge and practical readiness to integrate hydrogen technologies into their curricula and to discuss how vocational education can systematically prepare for the development of the hydrogen economy.

Throughout the day, participants explored:
✅ Fundamentals and safety aspects of hydrogen technologies
✅ Practical teaching tools and simulations (Energy Box, Hydrogen stand)
✅ Learning materials developed under the Green Skills for H2 initiative
✅ Practical approaches for integrating hydrogen topics into different technical disciplines

A key component of the training was a structured discussion on how to embed hydrogen-related competencies into automotive, energy, mechanical, and other technical study programmes in a consistent and sustainable manner.

The rapid evolution of the hydrogen value chain requires vocational education to adapt at the same pace. Empowering teachers with up-to-date knowledge and practical tools is essential to ensure high-quality, safe, and future-oriented professional training.

We thank all participants for their active engagement and valuable contributions, as well as the VOCO team for the excellent organisation of the event.

<a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fh2cove&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#H2CoVE</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fgreenskills4h2&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#GreenSkills4H2</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fhydrogen&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Hydrogen</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fvocationalexcellence&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#VocationalExcellence</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fvet&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#VET</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Ftartuvoco&amp;trk=organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="organization_guest_main-feed-card-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#TartuVOCO</a></p>
